comment: Whoa, just had a bit of a blast from the past. Dude I worked with at a grocery store 5+ years back just got hired on at my regular place.
Interrupted my apple appraisals, but we had a good chat.
Evidently, the store we worked to went to shit, had a new director every 6 months since shortly after my departure. In-Store politics went to the shitter as well.
